&lt;li&gt;Build and drive cost to serve analytics programs to guide engineering, finance, and leadership on the total cost (TCO) and infrastructure impact of our scaling factors. Inform pricing conversations through customer profile sensitive gross margin analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tech lead with outside vendors to manage anthropic capacity needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify infrastructure inefficiency opportunities, document proposal and be a key contributor in driving a positive outcome&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an advisor to engineering and finance functions and executive team for one of the largest areas of expenditure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with TPMs on special efficiency projects and help deliver committed outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
